channel.title: Darkchicken
channel.description:
yes that's his username, when i saw him he was with other lvl 120+'s (edgeville) but this dude could walk from point a to b, blinking so that you see his character for a split second and disappears for the other fraction of the second. He even had other people follow him the entire way while he was doing the routine. Its odd, i haven't seen anything quite like it. how does he do this though? :confused:
ps he's not a mod at the time
